<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Reactivated Successfully</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #00466a;">Xuthority</h2>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em;">
            Hi <%= userName %>,
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #28a745; font-weight: bold;">
            üéâ Welcome Back! Your Subscription is Reactivated
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            Great news! Your <strong><%= planName %></strong> subscription has been successfully reactivated. We're thrilled to have you back and you now have full access to all your premium features again!
        </p>

        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #155724;">
                üìã Subscription Details:
            </p>
            <div style="color: #666;">
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Plan:</strong> <%= planName %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Price:</strong> <%= planPrice %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Reactivated On:</strong> <%= reactivatedDate %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Next Billing Date:</strong> <%= nextBillingDate %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Billing Cycle:</strong> <%= billingCycle %></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #155724; font-weight: bold;">
                ‚úÖ All Premium Features Restored
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #155724;">
                Your account has been upgraded back to premium status. All your previous settings, data, and configurations have been preserved and are immediately available.
            </p>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            <strong>You now have access to:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul style="font-size: 1em; color: #666; margin-left: 20px;">
            <% if (features && features.length > 0) { %>
                <% features.forEach(function(feature) { %>
                <li><%= feature %></li>
                <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
            <li>Enhanced branding and profile customization</li>
            <li>Advanced analytics and business insights</li>
            <li>Priority customer support</li>
            <li>Unlimited product listings</li>
            <li>Lead generation and marketing tools</li>
            <li>Advanced search and filtering options</li>
            <li>Detailed performance reports</li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>

        <% if (wasDowntime) { %>
        <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #856404; font-weight: bold;">
                üìä Your Data is Safe
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #856404;">
                During your subscription pause, all your data, customer relationships, and account history were safely preserved. Everything is exactly as you left it!
            </p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" 
               style="background-color: #00466a; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 10px;">
                Go to Dashboard
            </a>
            <a href="<%= subscriptionUrl %>" 
               style="background-color: #6c757d; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
                Manage Subscription
            </a>
        </div>

        <% if (specialWelcomeBack) { %>
        <div style="background-color: #e7f3ff; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #004085; font-weight: bold;">
                üéÅ Welcome Back Bonus!
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #004085;">
                <%= specialWelcomeBack %>
            </p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            <strong>What's Next?</strong>
        </p>
        <ul style="font-size: 1em; color: #666; margin-left: 20px;">
            <li>Check out any new features we've added since your last visit</li>
            <li>Review and update your business profile</li>
            <li>Explore enhanced analytics and insights</li>
            <li>Reconnect with your customers and leads</li>
            <li>Take advantage of our latest marketing tools</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            <strong>Need Help Getting Back Up to Speed?</strong><br>
            Our support team is standing by to help you make the most of your reactivated subscription. We can provide a quick refresher on new features or help you optimize your account settings. Contact us at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #00466a;"><%= supportEmail %></a>.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            Thank you for choosing to continue your journey with Xuthority. We're committed to helping your business succeed and grow!
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            Best regards,<br>
            The Xuthority Team
        </p>

        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 10px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #aaa;">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><%= companyAddress %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 